<subSubSection pageId="101" pageNumber="102" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="101.[151,1436,1762,1943]" pageId="101" pageNumber="102">
<emphasis box="[151,233,1764,1789]" italics="true" pageId="101" pageNumber="102">Leaves</emphasis>
undivided or irregularly pinnate (sometimes with 1-veined pinnae present), plicate; rachis 70.7(44.5– 98.0) cm long; pinnae 2(1–4) per side of rachis; basal pinna 27.8(20.0–34.0) cm wide, forming an angle of 13(4–20)° with the rachis. 
<emphasis box="[464,632,1839,1865]" italics="true" pageId="101" pageNumber="102">Inflorescences</emphasis>
rachillae 14(8–30).
</paragraph>
